ActCanada Transportation Act
SubjectCanada-Michigan Agreement on the Detroit River International Crossing (DRIC)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Transport to enter into a crossing agreement in order to establish a framework for the design, construction, financing, operation and maintenance of a new international crossing between WINDSOR, Ontario and DETROIT, Michigan.
